    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，时间格式用M/D/YYYY，坐标轴显示为周数比如%W。那第一个section我放一个叫\"Wk 1\"的关键里程碑，标记为红色，持续一周，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section",
        "Wk 1",
        "crit",
        "weekblock"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，第一周作为起始标记。然后第二个section叫\"Topics\"，里面放五个教学模块。第一个是ER Models，从1月7号开始，持续三周。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Topics",
        "ER Models",
        "m1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，ER Models已添加，标记为m1。接下来是Rel. Algebra吧？我让它接在m1后面，持续两周。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rel. Algebra",
        "m4",
        "after m1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错。然后是Normal forms，三周；接着SQL模块四周；最后Adv. SQL五周。每个都顺序依赖前一个模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Normal forms",
        "SQL",
        "Adv. SQL",
        "m5",
        "m6",
        "m7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Normal forms接在m4后，标记m5；SQL接m5后，标记m6，持续四周；Adv. SQL接m6后，标记m7，持续五周。这样整个链条就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "m5",
        "m6",
        "m7",
        "after m4",
        "after m5",
        "after m6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，确认一下时间跨度——ER Models三周，Rel. Algebra两周，Normal forms三周，SQL四周，Adv. SQL五周，加起来覆盖整个学期，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ER Models",
        "Rel. Algebra",
        "Normal forms",
